General.Name: Jade Gas Holdings Ltd
General.Description: Jade Gas Holdings Limited engages in the exploration and appraisal of coal bed methane projects in Mongolia. Its flagship property is the Tavantolgoi coal bed methane project covering approximately 665 square kilometers located in the South Gobi region of Mongolia. The company is based in Kent Town, Australia.
